        "english": "But FUWAMOCO, a very Happy Birthday to you both!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:02.300",
        "end": "04:04.200",
        "original": "わぁー！ありがとう！",
        "english": "Wow! Thank you!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:04.300",
        "end": "04:05.600",
        "original": "おめでとうしんよー！バウバウ！",
        "english": "Happy birthday! Bau Bau!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:05.700",
        "end": "04:09.100",
        "original": "キュンからのバッキューン！おめでとうハート！",
        "english": "From kyun to bakkyun! Happy birthday heart!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:09.600",
        "end": "04:11.200",
        "original": "レッツゴー！",
        "english": "Let's go!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:17.300",
        "end": "04:18.500",
        "original": "花火だー！",
        "english": "Fireworks!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:18.600",
        "end": "04:21.800",
        "original": "ペロの花火だー！わぁー、きれいー！",
        "english": "It's Pero fireworks! Wow, so pretty!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:22.500",
        "end": "04:24.400",
        "original": "たまやー！",
        "english": "Tamaya!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:24.500",
        "end": "04:26.500",
        "original": "かぎやー！バウバウ！",
        "english": "Kagiya! Bau Bau!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:27.200",
        "end": "04:28.100",
        "original": "わぁー！",
        "english": "Wow!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:29.400",
        "end": "04:30.400",
        "original": "すごーい！",
        "english": "Amazing!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:30.500",
        "end": "04:32.400",
        "original": "わぁー、本当にきれい！",
        "english": "Wow, they're so beautiful!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:32.500",
        "end": "04:34.400",
        "original": "空が本当にすごいことになってるけど",
        "english": "The sky has really gone crazy,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:34.500",
        "end": "04:36.400",
        "original": "何が起こったのかよくわかんないよ！",
        "english": "but I'm not quite sure what happened!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:36.500",
        "end": "04:38.400",
        "original": "色がホントすごすぎて分からなくなってきたかも！",
        "english": "The colors are so intense I might be losing it!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:38.500",
        "end": "04:41.400",
        "original": "でも、まだもう一個すごく楽しみなことがあるんだよ！",
        "english": "But we still have one more very exciting thing to do!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:41.500",
        "end": "04:44.400",
        "original": "まだまだ楽しみがあるよ！",
        "english": "There's still more fun to come!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:44.500",
        "end": "04:46.400",
        "original": "わぁー！",
        "english": "Wow!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:48.500",
        "end": "04:51.400",
        "original": "何かなー？何かなー？",
        "english": "I wonder what it is? What is it?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:54.400",
        "end": "04:57.400",
        "original": "フワモコの1周年記念だよ！",
        "english": "It's FUWAMOCO's first anniversary!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      }
